reviewText:
Excellent Japanese DVD with the following videos:

1.  A-Ha - Take On Me
2.  Wham! - Wake Me Up Before You Go-Go
3.  Bananarama - Venus
4.  Rick Astley - Together Forever
5.  Chaka Khan - I Feel For You
6.  Cyndi Lauper - Time After Time
7.  Chicago - Hard To Say I'm Sorry
8.  Howard Jones - New Song
9.  Strawberry Switchblade - Since Yesterday
10.  Debbie Gibson - Lost In Your Eyes
11.  Frankie Goes To Hollywood - Relax
12.  Phil Collins - One More Night
13.  Twisted Sister - We're Not Gonna Take It (Full Version)
14.  Laura Branigan - Gloria
15.  Styx - Mr. Roboto
16.  Fine Young Cannibals - She Drives Me Crazy
17.  Yes - Owner Of A Lonely Heart (Full Version)
18.  Dream Academy - Life In A Northern Town
19.  Natalie Cole - Miss You Like Crazy

All videos are clean, full quality, 4:3, NTSC, and with crystal clear LPCM audio.  No tags or logos either.  To my knowledge, this is the only retail DVD with native NTSC copies of Chaka Khan's 'I Feel For You', Debbie Gibson's 'Lost In Your Eyes', and Laura Branigan's 'Gloria'.
